data.name: sqlInsertCommand1.CommandText
data.value: INSERT INTO [posmsg] ([mgsdate], [mgsdate1], [mgsdate2], [mgedate], [mgedate1], [mgedate2], [mgTitle], [message], [AppNo]) VALUES (@mgsdate, @mgsdate1, @mgsdate2, @mgedate, @mgedate1, @mgedate2, @mgTitle, @message, @AppNo); SELECT mgID, mgsdate, mgsdate1, mgsdate2, mgedate, mgedate1, mgedate2, mgTitle, message, AppNo FROM PosMsg WHERE (mgID = SCOPE_IDENTITY())

data.name: sqlUpdateCommand1.CommandText
data.value: UPDATE [posmsg] SET [mgsdate] = @mgsdate, [mgsdate1] = @mgsdate1, [mgsdate2] = @mgsdate2, [mgedate] = @mgedate, [mgedate1] = @mgedate1, [mgedate2] = @mgedate2, [mgTitle] = @mgTitle, [message] = @message, [AppNo] = @AppNo WHERE (([mgID] = @Original_mgID) AND ((@IsNull_mgsdate = 1 AND [mgsdate] IS NULL) OR ([mgsdate] = @Original_mgsdate)) AND ((@IsNull_mgsdate1 = 1 AND [mgsdate1] IS NULL) OR ([mgsdate1] = @Original_mgsdate1)) AND ((@IsNull_mgsdate2 = 1 AND [mgsdate2] IS NULL) OR ([mgsdate2] = @Original_mgsdate2)) AND ((@IsNull_mgedate = 1 AND [mgedate] IS NULL) OR ([mgedate] = @Original_mgedate)) AND ((@IsNull_mgedate1 = 1 AND [mgedate1] IS NULL) OR ([mgedate1] = @Original_mgedate1)) AND ((@IsNull_mgedate2 = 1 AND [mgedate2] IS NULL) OR ([mgedate2] = @Original_mgedate2)) AND ((@IsNull_mgTitle = 1 AND [mgTitle] IS NULL) OR ([mgTitle] = @Original_mgTitle)) AND ((@IsNull_message = 1 AND [message] IS NULL) OR ([message] = @Original_message)) AND ((@IsNull_AppNo = 1 AND [AppNo] IS NULL) OR ([AppNo] = @Original_AppNo))); SELECT mgID, mgsdate, mgsdate1, mgsdate2, mgedate, mgedate1, mgedate2, mgTitle, message, AppNo FROM PosMsg WHERE (mgID = @mgID)
